          <content>
            <p>Sec. 12-502a. Administrative provisions. Penalties. Hearings and appeals.The provisions of sections12-548to12-554, inclusive, and section12-555ashall apply to the provisions of sections12-494to12-504, inclusive, in the same manner and with the same force and effect as if the language of said sections12-548to12-554, inclusive, and section12-555ahad been incorporated in full into said sections and had expressly referred to the tax imposed under said sections, except to the extent that any such provision is inconsistent with a provision of said sections.
